Nemysli si, že ti to dáva právo, jej vziať panenstvo.

229
00:17:38,020 --> 00:17:40,200
Už len na to som myslel!

230
00:17:40,200 --> 00:17:42,120
Čo ti povedal?

231
00:17:42,120 --> 00:17:44,320
N-Nič!

232
00:17:44,320 --> 00:17:46,320
Nie je to tak!

233
00:17:48,240 --> 00:17:51,620
Ale asi to je v poriadku...

234
00:17:51,620 --> 00:17:53,840
Nateraz...

235
00:17:55,590 --> 00:17:59,760
...budem môcť zas s Reou ži-

236
00:18:03,380 --> 00:18:06,330
Furuya-kun?

237
00:18:06,330 --> 00:18:07,600
Furuya-kun!

238
00:18:08,060 --> 00:18:10,110
Nie!

239
00:18:15,060 --> 00:18:16,260
Chceli by ste niečo na pitie?

240
00:18:16,260 --> 00:18:16,860
Nie.

241
00:18:43,550 --> 00:18:45,220
Vďaka bohu.

242
00:18:47,870 --> 00:18:48,730
Prepáč!

243
00:18:53,050 --> 00:18:55,610
Hm? Vrátilo sa mi vnímanie bolesti.

244
00:18:56,480 --> 00:18:57,550
Chápem.

245
00:18:57,550 --> 00:19:00,210
Tak ten jed už musí byť z môjho tela vonku!

246
00:19:00,210 --> 00:19:02,230
Sakra, to bolí!

247
00:19:02,230 --> 00:19:05,380
Ošetrili sme ti rany.

248
00:19:05,380 --> 00:19:07,750
Vyzerá to tak, že si sa vrátil zo záhrobia.

249
00:19:08,150 --> 00:19:10,000
Hej, ja som vôbec nebol mŕtvy!

250
00:19:11,720 --> 00:19:13,550
Každopádne, som rada, že si v poriadku!

251
00:19:13,550 --> 00:19:18,090
Stratil si toľko krvi... už som si myslela, že sa nikdy nezobudíš...

252
00:19:18,090 --> 00:19:21,510
Asi hej... bála si sa o mňa. Prepáč.

253
00:19:22,830 --> 00:19:24,010
Vôbec nie.

254
00:19:27,620 --> 00:19:29,930
Hej, ten kostým.

255
00:19:30,380 --> 00:19:36,550
Slúžky mi povedali, že by sa ti mohol páčiť...

256
00:19:37,710 --> 00:19:40,110
Nie je dobrý?

257
00:19:40,110 --> 00:19:44,620
Zombie sestrička! Dokonalé!

258
00:19:45,010 --> 00:19:47,490
Nii nemôže niečomu takému odolať...

259
00:19:47,810 --> 00:19:49,750
Chihiro!

260
00:19:50,280 --> 00:19:50,960
Ranko.

261
00:19:51,860 --> 00:19:53,580
Ty idiot!

262
00:19:53,950 --> 00:19:57,090
Dobehla som sem hneď, ako mi Mero-chan povedala, že si zranený!

263
00:19:57,090 --> 00:20:00,180
Tak keď vieš, že som zranený, tak po mne neskáč!

264
00:20:00,180 --> 00:20:02,020
Ah, prepáč.

265
00:20:02,020 --> 00:20:04,550
Čo sa vlastne stalo?

266
00:20:04,550 --> 00:20:06,490
N-Nuž...

267
00:20:09,130 --> 00:20:10,990
P-Prepáč.

268
00:20:10,990 --> 00:20:14,100
To všetko je moja vina...

269
00:20:14,580 --> 00:20:17,040
Hm? Prečo si oblečená ako sestrička?

270
00:20:17,040 --> 00:20:20,040
Povedali mi, že by sa to Furuyovi-kun mohlo páčiť.

271
00:20:20,040 --> 00:20:22,850
Hej, čo ju to nútiš robiť, ty perverzák!

272
00:20:22,850 --> 00:20:24,610
Ja som ju to nenútil si obliecť!

273
00:20:24,610 --> 00:20:26,340
Ale páči sa ti to.

274
00:20:26,340 --> 00:20:27,620
To teda he-

275
00:20:27,620 --> 00:20:29,080
Hej, čo ma to nútiš povedať?!

276
00:20:29,080 --> 00:20:30,440
Huh...

277
00:20:30,440 --> 00:20:35,030
Každopádne, Furuya-kun takto dopadol kvôli mne.

278
00:20:35,030 --> 00:20:36,840
Rea, nemusíš sa-

279
00:20:41,740 --> 00:20:46,040
Sanka-san, správne? Ty si ten zombie, čo tu teraz žije?

280
00:20:46,040 --> 00:20:47,850
A-Áno...

281
00:20:50,500 --> 00:20:53,350
Oh, ešte som sa ti nepredstavila, že?

282
00:20:54,390 --> 00:20:57,650
Som Ranko Saoji. Som o rok staršia od teba.

283
00:20:59,310 --> 00:21:00,360
Rada ťa spoznávam.

284
00:21:00,840 --> 00:21:03,100
Som pre Chihira ako veľká sestra, a jej snúbenka!

285
00:21:04,380 --> 00:21:06,700
Jeho ľudská snúbenka, samozrejme.

286
00:21:10,070 --> 00:21:13,390
Chápeš, že to bol vtip, že?!

287
00:21:13,390 --> 00:21:16,990
Hej, Ranko... san... Nehovor také veci.

288
00:21:16,990 --> 00:21:18,050
Huh?

289
00:21:18,050 --> 00:21:21,380
Ale sľúbil si mi to ešte vtedy na základke.

290
00:21:22,770 --> 00:21:23,510
Chihiro!

291
00:21:23,980 --> 00:21:25,620
Čo?

292
00:21:25,620 --> 00:21:27,820
Buď mojim snúbencom!

293
00:21:27,820 --> 00:21:28,970
Čo to je?

294
00:21:29,480 --> 00:21:30,970
To je jedno. Len buď mojim snúbencom!

295
00:21:32,480 --> 00:21:33,980
Dobre teda...

296
00:21:34,810 --> 00:21:37,690
Ako keby som si pamätal nejaké takéto veci, o ktorých sme sa bavili!

297
00:21:38,340 --> 00:21:39,230
Robím si srandu.

298
00:21:39,590 --> 00:21:41,420
Prepáč, Sanka-san.

299
00:21:41,420 --> 00:21:42,860
Ale videla si to?

300
00:21:42,860 --> 00:21:45,550
Je rozkošný, keď je nervózny, že?

301
00:21:45,550 --> 00:21:46,530
Buď ticho!

302
00:21:46,530 --> 00:21:48,740
Pred chvíľou si v podstate ešte plakala!

303
00:21:49,490 --> 00:21:50,940
To som len hrala.

304
00:21:50,940 --> 00:21:53,820
Hej, jasne. Vlastne aj ja som to len hral.

305
00:21:53,820 --> 00:21:56,210
Tak to potom nebolo veľmi presvedčivé.

306
00:21:56,210 --> 00:21:57,500
Ale vieš...

307
00:21:58,600 --> 00:22:01,790
Čo keby si mi povedal celý príbeh?

308
00:22:01,790 --> 00:22:03,920
Možno, ak ma pustíš.

309
00:22:03,920 --> 00:22:05,110
To asi nebudem môcť urobiť!

310
00:22:05,110 --> 00:22:06,090
Chápem...
To asi nebudem môcť urobiť!

311
00:22:06,550 --> 00:22:07,720
To dievča...

312
00:22:08,360 --> 00:22:13,160
...má rada Furuyu-kuna.

